{"tid":1803263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲女單位內服藥昏迷 友人趕至惜已太遲","createTime":"2019-12-30T05:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T05:47:27.000Z","uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ee9bd66440aa2a9dd43f9eaa027038ba9d5926","tid":1803263,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"【12:44】新增內容<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣福華街568號一幢唐樓，昨晚11時許，一名女子在劏房單位內昏迷不醒，女友人稍後揭發報警，救護員趕至現場，惟證實女子已經死亡，警員在現場進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n女死者姓梁25歲，據悉患有情緒病，並因關注近日發生的抗爭活動而影響情緒。初步相信她因生活及情緒問題服藥自殺，昏迷後失救死亡，警員在屋內撿獲遺書，案件並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n有街坊向《蘋果》透露，梁女今年初才搬入，獨居上址一劏房單位。街坊見她平日多穿黑衫黑褲，但沒戴口罩，亦未聞她提及近半年的抗爭運動。但早兩個月，梁女曾服藥昏迷入院醫治。姓何街坊表示，「父母過嚟睇佢，但拍門唔應，拍咗兩個鐘，門都爛晒！最後要消防嚟開門，父母話佢食藥昏迷咗。」<br />\n<br />\n自該事件後，街坊一度以為她搬走，「因為佢父母講過想接佢返屋企住，唔想佢一個人喺出面。」何說平時不多見梁女出入，但今年初有一次見梁女在天台睡覺，就印象深刻，「有一次喺天台，佢夜晚拎住兩罐啤酒，喺天台食煙，仲爬出壆，冇嘢攔住，我話咁樣好危險，佢好似昏昏迷迷，我叫佢快啲返落嚟，佢後來醒咗返落嚟，都攪咗個幾兩個鐘。佢講嘢一嚿嚿，以為佢啪咗嘢，原來佢有抑鬱。」<br />\n<br />\n網上蘋果日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191230/60430351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191230%2F60430351&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=dc469acf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191230%2F60430351&h=bfd18861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191230/60430351</a><br />\n<br />\n會唔會曾經被黑警拉過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7765b18017238266c46985761aa60414f4310a","tid":1803263,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a84b7f88e8b8340bcb04a2c884f640294a0338","tid":1803263,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948cd2eaa43ed7ba8ad9dc462c54bb3b76d7cc0d","tid":1803263,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"⋯唉<br />\n睇完之後個人好激動"},{"pid":"e8ab05b041ac42b20ef59c3bed1d5f788ca81b5e","tid":1803263,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cffbb280482c6fbca6a70da853d298c9dfc91f","tid":1803263,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"兒登仔：手足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}